<paragraph blockId="7.[192,1440,1794,1882]" pageId="7" pageNumber="6">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,340,1794,1818]" pageId="7" pageNumber="6">Etymology</emphasis>
. We are pleased to name this species in honor of Marcela Laura Monné, for her friendship and many contributions to the study of Neotropical 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[833,1013,1826,1850]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Cerambycidae</taxonomicName>
. The epithet is a noun in the genitive case.
</paragraph>
<caption box="[233,1400,1837,1859]" pageId="8" pageNumber="7" startId="8.[233,317,1837,1859]" targetBox="[233,1400,192,1821]" targetPageId="8">
